<collectingCountry box="[1074,1151,242,264]" name="Sudan" pageId="12" pageNumber="12">Sudan</collectingCountry>
, 
<date pageId="12" pageNumber="12" value="1901-02-28">28 February 1901</date>
, by Rothschild and Wollaston (no. 171). While this specimen was not sexed in the field, the Rothschild label, written by Hartert, is marked â€˜â€˜ 
